Package: autograder
Title: Automated R Function Testing and Grading
Version: 0.3.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Agub", "Reijel", 
           email = "rcagub@up.edu.ph", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: 
    An automated grading system for R programming assignments with advanced
    features including parallel test execution, improved error handling, custom
    feedback, and AES encryption for test case protection. Securely fetches test
    cases from remote repositories and provides detailed feedback to students.
